greed upon) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3756,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/23\/ramadan-do-not-precede-fast\/","url_meta":{"origin":3795,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Do not fast days before Ramadan, unless a routine","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 23, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cLet not one of you precede Ramadan with one or two days of fasting, unless it is part of a man's fasting routine, so let him fast that day.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1815. S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1082\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14882,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/10\/eat-blessed-suhur\/","url_meta":{"origin":3795,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Suhur: Blessings in pre-fasting morning meal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 10, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTake the pre-fasting meal, for surely there are blessings in the pre-fasting meal.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1923, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1095 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\